cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DB 

The paper discusses the development of an automated and intelligent advertising system for sponsored search, which involves the use of machine learning techniques for bidding, targeting, and ad creation. This falls under the categories of information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI), and databases (cs.DB).
